1:1 COMMENT "# field_reassign.z -- Reassigning a reftype field with `=`"
1:59 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "#"
2:2 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "# `rec.field = v` destroys the old field value, moves `v` into the"
3:67 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# slot, and invalidates `v`. Equivalent to `rec.field.release;"
4:63 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# rec.field = v.take` collapsed into one statement."
5:52 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "#"
6:2 EOL "\n"
7:1 COMMENT "# Use `swap` instead when both the LHS and the RHS need to remain"
7:66 EOL "\n"
8:1 COMMENT "# initialised and addressable (no move occurs; the two slots exchange"
8:70 EOL "\n"
9:1 COMMENT "# contents)."
9:13 EOL "\n"
10:1 EOL "\n"
